{[#]White did not display any kingside space ambitions. As pointed out by
Nimzowitsch, any unpromoted pawn formation is likely to be submitted to the
attack. Black to move.} 21... f4 $17 {Indeed, this active move, involving
material sacrifices, offers Black overwheling initiative.} 22. gxf4 $2 ({
Playing into Blck's hands, the same as} 22. Bxf4 $2 Nxf4 23. gxf4 Qh4 $19 24.
