have accepted a strategically awfull position with, say,} 22. Nc2 fxg3+ 23.
fxg3 $17) 22... Qh4 $19 {There is no satisfactory defence already.} 23. Ra4 (
23. fxe5 Bxe5+ 24. f4 (24. Kg1 Bxh3) 24... Qg3+ 25. Kg1 Bxh3 26. Rf2 Bd4 27. e3
Rxe3 $1 28. Bxe3 Bxg2 $5 $19) (23. e3 Bg4 $19) (23. Nc2 {allos Black revealing
his main threat:} Bxh3 24. Bxh3 Nxf4 25. Bxf4 Qxf4+ 26. Kg2 Ng4 27. Bxg4 (27.
e3 Qh2+ 28. Kf3 Rf8+ 29. Ke2 Rxf2+ {mating soon.}) 27... Qxg4+ 28. Kh1 Re5 {
followed by ...Rh5 mate.}) 23... Rb4 24. Rxb4 cxb4 25. Qa4 Rf8 26. Qxb4 Nxf4
27. Bxf4 Rxf4 28. Qxd6 Ng4+ 29. Kg1 Nxf2 30. Qc5 Nxh3+ 31. Bxh3 Bd4+ 32. Qxd4
Rxd4 33. Bg2 Qg5 34. Nc2 Bh3 35. Kf2 Rg4 0-1

