dxe5 $1 15. d6+ Kh8 16. Ng5 e4 17. Ne6 Qf6 18. Nxf8 Qd4+ 19. Qxd4 Bxd4+ 20. Kh1
Nxf8 $15) 14... Nb6 15. Bb3 (15. Be2 a5 $5 {[%csl Gb4][%cal Gc5c4] is similar.}
) 15... a5 $5 {This secures the knight preparing ...c5-c4.} 16. Be3 (16. Ne6 $2
