{[#] If White manages to complete the development by making castle, Black will
be deprived of real counterplay. As it is always the case in Benoni type of
positions, Black should play very energetically.} 1... g5 $1 {With the new
queenside configurtion this is good now.} 2. Bxg5 Nxg5 3. Nxh5 Nh7 4. Nxg7 Kxg7
5. g4 Qb4 $1 {The main idea is to reduce the attacking potential with a
well-timed ...Qd4.} *

