{[#] White has managed to carry out the thematic e4-e5. How should Black react?
} 1... dxe5 $1 {Of course. Black should accept the challenge. In such kind of
positions, the control of the dark squares is much more important than the
missing exchange.} 2. fxe5 Rxe5 3. Bf4 Nfd7 $1 {With more than sufficient
compensation for the exchange. Later on, a knight transfer to d3 is a very
decent option.} *

