{[#] White threatens to win material but he is behind in the development. Try
to overtake the initiative.} 1... Bxf5 $1 {A very nice concrete approach to
the position. Now, White will have a hard time to deal with Black's growing
initiative.} 2. Nxa8 Nxf3+ $1 {Keeping the momentum! In such a dynamic
position, regaining material is not an option.} 3. gxf3 Qxe3 {With ...Ng5 to
follow. Black has more than sufficient compensation for the sacrificed
material.} *

