{[#] White intends to establish an annoying blockade on c4. Black should find
a dynamic way to deal with this idea.} 1... b3 $1 2. Qb1 g5 3. Bg3 Nxd5 $1 {
This is what happens if too many pieces step back. Now, White is forced to go
for the following sequence:} 4. Nc4 Nf4 5. Bxf4 gxf4 6. Nxd6 Re6 {Material is
equal but the structure is unusual. Black's activity compensates for the pawn
weaknesses.} *

